    "While ChatGPT can provide guidance on these operations, it frequently deviates from the precise steps we take.",
    "Consequently, it is necessary to explore whether ChatGPT truly comprehends the algorithms involved in these tasks or if it is simply generating sentences without a thorough understanding.",
